title: Marvin Gaye The Complete Sessions - Rare
description:
Marvin Gaye (The Sessions) & Rare Recordings

Here is a collection of all of Marvin Gaye's sessions and Bonus Material from all the expanded and Special Editions. Also included are unreleased tracks and rare compositions that are unavailable or out of print.

What's Going On (Detroit Mix) 10 Tracks
What's Going On (Single Mixes) 3 Tracks
Let's Get It On (The Sessions) 9 Tracks
I Want You (The Sessions) 11 Tracks
I Want You (Bonus Tracks) 6 Tracks
Here, My Dear (Alternative Mixes & Bonus Tracks) 14 Tracks
Love Man (The Recordings Re-Mastered) 6 Tracks
In Our Lifetime? (Odyssey Mixes) 8 Tracks
In Our Lifetime? (Bonus Tracks) 4 Tracks
Sexual Healing (The Sessions) 17 Tracks

and

Bonus Recordings, Rock Savage Remixes, Compositions, Acapellas & Unreleased Songs (26 Tracks)

All tracks are Mp3 320 kbps Tagged with Original Art Work

I am thinking of producing a set of Marvin's Live Recordings so Holla if this moves you.

Enjoy the greatest musical artist of all time!!!!

With Love Rock Savage
